":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c9e7e9cc52b2038ddd9eda47fda5a94bef0a52e","tid":1674014,"uid":150014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T03:35:07.000Z","msg":"陳坤耀，唔係陳耀坤"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T03:38:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2676601b352bace6daf3847b69b076a6f7ec4750","tid":1674014,"uid":65604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T03:39:12.000Z","msg":"虛偽，夠薑咪同何妖握手合照一張囉，横掂何妖都要選舉，話你陳耀坤真心推薦比街坊囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12cd989c6d57a5c8a4fb2ebb40ff72d9ecc15c72","tid":1674014,"uid":60279,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ba408525ff3554f53b1b198dce2f2e612bce16f6","tid":1674014,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b17117091717fb7fb2333118e689c75bf1c3ed44","tid":1674014,"uid":60279,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c8fd0bf7b30fa474619b541e0b8e850094d810fe","tid":1674014,"uid":73269,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T03:26:27.000Z","msg":"元朗襲擊只是事實的假設<br />\n難聽過粗口"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T03:31:40.000Z","msg":"你唔好曲解人地意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人地唔係話元朗721本身係事實的假設<br />\n係「條撚樣有份」依樣野係事實的假設"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T03:33:14.000Z","msg":"括弧裏面啲字係記者加上去"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T03:39:54.000Z","msg":"公眾懷疑何君堯和721白衣人關係，對於何君堯有否損害嶺大校譽<br />\n<br />\n記者係有前題下問佢, 姐係記者, 校長都知條問題係問緊<br />\n條撚樣 同 721 有無直接關係<br />\n所以校長先話 「條撚樣有份」依樣野係事實的假設<br />\n作為校長佢咁答係應該, 因為事實真係無人拉佢, 無直接証據指向條撚樣<br />\n<br />\n但係作為人 咁答當然係仆街啦"},{"pid":"30846c0698bb6e013add622d09ea3517e1857656","tid":1674014,"uid":19676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c2da5dabc135761afe80b0a21c8588e5bc50f5a","tid":1674014,"uid":77196,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T03:23:49.000Z","msg":"佢老母個墳都爛撚埋就知咩事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T03:41:41.000Z","msg":"個墳爛左都係事實假設<br />\n唔好周圍瀨呀"},{"pid":"4bcf05eb0203cc4e1cd85169da9b1c00deab62e4","tid":1674014,"uid":60279,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"a43eea917a40ce95765903fbb430802dd5af4f47","tid":1674014,"uid":152934,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T03:33:36.000Z","msg":"&quot;我們只有事實的假設&quot;<br />\n佢講到咁其實都<span style=\"color: red;\">acknowledge 左件事</span><br />\n只係冇證據 吹何妖唔漲<br />\n係要奶共既 根本都唔洗講咩假設 直頭講話冇發生過／唔講<br />\n再換句話說 即係現階段唔夠證據罷免唔到<br />\n中肯d講 咁佢事實上又冇講錯<br />\n要插佢既 只能夠等有更多證據 睇佢再講咩.."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T03:42:47.000Z","msg":"其實都講到好白<br />\n<br />\n無証據話撚樣真係有份 所以佢唔可能炒撚樣<br />\n佢做到最盡都係唔比佢參與每一個委員會<br />\n姐係變相廢左佢權力<br />\n<br />\n不過係咪真係做得出又一回事"},{"pid":"77443c3e9d6954293070850c98f43eab6905ad3f","tid":1674014,"uid":307662,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T03:43:01.000Z","msg":"佢冇被拘捕純粹因為警方包庇吾起訴佢<br />\n警方包庇佢係因為警方自己有份策劃襲擊"},{"pid":"0bce5729fb1490693a1510301a49195337da3d31","tid":1674014,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2676601b352bace6daf3847b69b076a6f7ec4750","tid":1674014,"uid":65604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T03:39:12.000Z","msg":"虛偽，夠薑咪同何妖握手合照一張囉，横掂何妖都要選舉，話你陳耀坤真心推薦比街坊囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T03:43:43.000Z","msg":"嶺南大學嘅管理層<br />\n就上下一心撐何君堯<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/files/styles/w775/public/column_images/40_1.jpg?itok=8ShO5bCb\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Fw775%2Fpublic%2Fcolumn_images%2F40_1.jpg%3Fitok%3D8ShO5bCb&h=d07ff619&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4438/37131396630_69e70325e9.jpg\" data-thumbnail